import sqlContext.implicits._
import org.apache.spark.sql.Row;
import org.apache.spark.sql.types.{StructType,StructField,StringType};
import java.text.SimpleDateFormat

def cacheJSON(table: String) :Unit ={
  val name = table.replace("-", "_") + "_raw"
  sqlContext.sql("drop table if exists " + name)
  sqlContext.read.json(fs+table+"/*").createOrReplaceTempView(name+"_tmp")
  sqlContext.sql("select input_file_name() as fn, * from " + name + "_tmp").coalesce(1).write.format("parquet")
    .mode("overwrite").option("path", fs+"derived/"+name).saveAsTable(name)
  println("Wrote " + name + " to " + fs+"derived/"+name)
  sqlContext.cacheTable(name)
  println("Cached " + name)
  sqlContext.sql("drop table " + name + "_tmp")
}

def cacheTable(query: String, table: String) :Unit = {
  sqlContext.sql("drop table if exists " + table)
  sqlContext.sql(query).coalesce(1).write.format("parquet")
    .mode("overwrite").option("path", fs+"derived/"+table).saveAsTable(table)
  println("Wrote " + table + " to "+fs+"derived/"+table)
  sqlContext.cacheTable(table)
  println("Cached table "+table)
}

val nmon_raw = sc.wholeTextFiles(fs+"host-data/metrics/nmon/*")
case class nmonRec(node: String, ts: String, CPUUser: Double, CPUSys: Double, MemFree: Long, MemAvailable: Long, MemTotal: Long, DiskBusy: Double)

nmon_raw.filter(_._2 contains "ZZZZ").map(x => {
    val lines = x._2.split("\n")
    nmonRec(
      x._1.split("/").last.split("_").head, //node
      lines.filter(_ contains "ZZZZ")(0).split(",")(3) + " " +
      lines.filter(_ contains "ZZZZ")(0).split(",")(2), //timestamp
      lines.filter(y => y.contains("T0001") && y.startsWith("CPU_ALL"))(0).split(",")(2).trim.toDouble, // User CPU
      lines.filter(y => y.contains("T0001") && y.startsWith("CPU_ALL"))(0).split(",")(3).trim.toDouble, // Sys CPU
      lines.filter(y => y.contains("MemFree"))(0).split(": ")(1).split(" kB")(0).trim.toLong,
      lines.filter(y => y.contains("MemAvailable"))(0).split(": ")(1).split(" kB")(0).trim.toLong,
      lines.filter(y => y.contains("MemTotal"))(0).split(": ")(1).split(" kB")(0).trim.toLong,
      lines.filter(y => y.contains("DISKBUSY"))(1).split(",")(2).trim.toDouble
    )
}).toDF().coalesce(1).createOrReplaceTempView("nmon_raw")

%sql
create table if not exists metrics as
select
  concat(date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm'), ':00') as time,
  round(avg(cpuuser + cpusys)) as CPUUsed,
  round(avg(diskbusy)) as DISKUsed,
  round(avg(memavailable/memtotal)*100) as RAMUsed,
  round(avg(memavailable)/1000) as MemAvailable,
  sum(b.requests) as InternalRequests,
  sum(c.requests) as ExternalRequests,
  sum((b.requests + c.requests)) as TotalRequests
from node_monitoring a
join (
  select
    date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time,
    1 as requests
  from web_logs_enriched
  where source_host is not null or source_ip = '127.0.0.1'
) b on date_format(a.datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') = b.time
join (
  select 
    date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') as time,
    1 as requests
  from web_logs_enriched
  where source_host is null  
) c on date_format(a.datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm') = c.time
group by date_format(datetime, 'yyyy-MM-dd HH:mm')
order by time asc
